## How to Play

1. Download the Pixelmelon Client(https://github.com/AssasinDev/pixelmelon-client)
2. Download the version folder you want to play.  
3. Extract it if needed.
4. Create a folder where you will put the version folder(the .exe and .pck are required to be in the folder).
5. In the Pixelmelon Client in "Versions Folder" click "Browse" and search your folder where all the version folders are.
6. Select your version in "Select Version".
7. Select your rendering drivers on "Rendering Driver".
8. Optionally you can add launch options.
9. Press the Launch button to run the executable.  
10. Enjoy the game!  

- Versions may have bugs and others things. Feedback will be appreciated.  
